name: MentalDisorders
title: Mental Disorders
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This grouping of value sets identifies patients who have a mental disorder.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have a mental disorder.  Using the Quality Data Model, this data element maps to the Diagnosis category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Only include codes which represent a mental disorder.  This is a grouping of ICD9CM, ICD10CM and SNOMED-CT codes and concepts.),(Exclusion Criteria: Exclude codes that do not meet the inclusion criteria.)
